# m5_p16_hud_smoke.shot — M5 P16
#
# HUD verification: HP bar, jet bar, armor pip, weapon icon + ammo,
# kill-feed lane, crosshair. Single Trooper standing still on default
# map with a weapon equipped + the secondary slot shown in kill-feed
# preview. Fires once at tick 30 so a kill-feed entry appears for
# the verification frame.
#
# Run:
#   ./soldut --shot tests/shots/m5_p16_hud_smoke.shot
# Output:
#   build/shots/m5_p16_hud_smoke/hud.png
#
# Verification:
#   - the log shows `hud: atlas loaded (256x256)`
#   - the rendered PNG shows:
#     * HP bar (cyan/blue) bottom-left with `HP: 150 / 150` text
#     * Jet bar below HP in a different tone
#     * Armor pip "Light 36" tag
#     * `[1] Pulse Rifle 30 / 30` ammo + `[2] Frag Grenades` secondary
#       at bottom-right with weapon icons
#     * Crosshair near cursor (`+` shape, cyan when bink low)

window 1280 720
seed   3 5
out    build/shots/m5_p16_hud_smoke

loadout Trooper "Pulse Rifle" "Frag Grenades" Medium Heavy
spawn_at 1060 984
mouse    700 400

at  30 tap fire
at  60 shot hud
at  90 end
